```

**Detection rationale:**

| Condition | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `[INST]` present | Identifies Mistral-family templates |
| `[AVAILABLE_TOOLS]` present | Distinguishes V3-era from V1 and llama2 (which lack tool support markers) |
| `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` absent | Distinguishes from Ministral 3, V7, Devstral (which use separate system block) |
