**File:** `tests/test-chat.cpp`  
**Location:** The existing Nemo test block at lines 3139-3148 will now route through the specialized handler instead of the autoparser. Verify existing tests still pass and add parallel tool call test.

Existing tests (should still pass as-is):
```cpp
